              </div>
            </Prose>
          </div>
          <Image src={Lukas} alt="Lukas Lehmann" width={300}  class="rounded-3xl rotate-3 mx-4 md:mx-0"/>
        </div>     
        <div>
          <h2>Role</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Digital Product Designer</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
         <div>
          <h2>Mission</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Creating accessible digital experiences for neurodivergent users.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Demographics</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Location:</strong> <del>Jerusalem, Israel</del> Berlin, Germany</li>
            <li><strong>Languages:</strong> German (Native), English (Fluent), Hebrew (Professional)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Education</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Currently enhancing my Product UX Design skills</strong> at WBS CODING SCHOOL (July 2024 - November 2024)</li>
            <li><strong>Certified in UX/UI Design and Scrum Master (PSM I)</strong> from cimdata Bildungsakademie (July 2023 - March 2024)</li>
            <li><strong>BA in Jewish Studies</strong>, which taught me strong research skills and analytical thinking (HfJS Heidelberg, 2005 - 2011)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Work Experience</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Transitioned from disability work, website management and publishing</strong> to UX/UI design</li>
