          <ul>
            <li><strong>Accessible UX/UI Design:</strong> Inclusive design for all users and devices</li>
            <li><strong>Responsive Web Design:</strong> Mobile-first, fluid layouts, and media queries</li>
            <li><strong>Design Systems:</strong> Consistent design patterns and reusable components</li>
            <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Design Sprint, Design Thinking and remote team communication</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Tech Stacks</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Design Tools:</strong> Figma, Sketch, and Adobe XD</li>
            <li><strong>SEO:</strong> Structured data, meta tags, and sitemaps</li>
            <li><strong>Content Management:</strong> WordPress, Obsidian and Astro framework</li>
            <li><strong>HTML/CSS:</strong> Semantic markup, BEM, and CSS Grid/Flexbox</li>
            <li><strong>Version Control:</strong> Git and GitHub</li>
            <li><strong>Command Line:</strong> Terminal, npm, and build tools</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Certifications</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Product UX Design:</strong> WBS Coding School (July 2024 - November 2024)</li>
            <li><strong>UX/UI Design & Scrum Master (PSM I):</strong> cimdata Bildungsakademie (July 2023 - March 2024)</li>
            <li><strong>Content Marketing Manager:</strong> WBS Training AG (October 2021 - July 2022)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Strengh</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Deep understanding of diverse user needs</strong> from my work in disability support</li>
            <li><strong>Wide range of skills</strong> from working in different industries, including project management, problem-solving, and clear communication</li>
            <li><strong>Skilled in design tools:</strong> Figma, Adobe XD, Sketch</li>
            <li><strong>Unique perspective as a neurodivergent designer</strong>, helping to create new and creative solutions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Motivation</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Passionate about creating digital products</strong> that are both functional and inclusive</li>
            <li><strong>Excited to apply my skills</strong> in accessibility-focused UX/UI design and product development</li>
            <li><strong>Eager to work on projects</strong> that focus on accessibility and user-centered design</li>
            <li><strong>Committed to continuous learning</strong> and staying updated with UX design trends</li>
            <li><strong>Ready to collaborate</strong> with your team to create impactful, user-friendly solutions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        </div>
        </article>
      </article>
    </main>
  </div>
